Apache2 Server

1. Start  
   sudo systemctl start apache2.service

2. Stop
   sudo systemctl stop apache2.service

3. Restart
   sudo systemctl restart apache2.service
   
4. Check status star/stop/restart
   journalctl -u apache2
   
5. Check whether apache2 is running OR not
   sudo systemctl status apache2.service
   
6. Check apache2 server version
   apache2 -v
   

Tutorial source : https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/ubuntu-linux-start-restart-stop-apache-web-server/
